<p class="tag">Forge swords. Slay the horde. — a dark-fantasy idle merge RPG by Support Ethics Ltd.</p>

<h2>Need help?</h2>
<div class="card">
  <p><strong>Email us:</strong> <a href="mailto:sean@support-ethics.co.uk">sean@support-ethics.co.uk</a><br>
