<h2>Common questions</h2>
<p><strong>My purchase didn't arrive.</strong> Open the in-game SHOP, scroll to the
bottom of the DEALS tab and tap <strong>RESTORE</strong>. If it still doesn't appear,
email us with your App Store receipt.</p>
<p><strong>I got a new phone — where's my progress?</strong> Your save lives on your
device. Purchases (Remove Ads, premium skins and swords) can always be restored with
the RESTORE button on any device signed into your store account.</p>
<p><strong>How do I stop seeing ads?</strong> Ad breaks can be removed forever with the
one-time <strong>Remove Ads</strong> purchase in the shop. Reward ads are always
